import numpy as np

In [8]:
coffee = Image.open('coffee.jpg')
#print (coffee.mode)

print ('coffee (RGB)')
plt.imshow(coffee)
plt.show()

r, g, b, = coffee.split()

print ('red channel')
plt.imshow(r)
plt.show()

print ('green channel')
plt.imshow(g)
plt.show()

print ('blue channel')
plt.imshow(b)
plt.show()

#print (texture.mode)

print ('texture (RGB)')
plt.imshow(texture)
plt.show()

rT, gT, bT, = texture.split()

print ('red channel')
plt.imshow(rT)
plt.show()

print ('green channel')
plt.imshow(gT)
plt.show()

print ('blue channel')
plt.imshow(bT)
plt.show()
